      "rationale": "NIH and relative hemolysis index RH are the standard regulatory quantities for blood pump hemolysis assessment per FDA guidance. Direct mapping from computational QoI to clinical endpoint established. Gradation 2 met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
